                <h3><strong>SEAS</strong></h3>
                <p>South East Asian Cuisine | 12:00 pm - 22:00 pm</p>
                <p>Dress code: Resort Smart Casual | <a href="https://webbox-assets.siteminder.com/assets/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/3b732d4b-f884-458b-a9a4-aa3c571004ba.pdf">Menu</a></p>
                <div> Overlooking the uplit oasis of oneeighty° and the Indian Ocean beyond,&nbsp; <strong>seas</strong> restaurant is the showcase of acclaimed Balinese Chef Nyoman Suasa.&nbsp;Long at the vanguard of ‘New Indonesian’ cuisine and the culinary mind behind the&nbsp;opening of Seminyak’ s renowned Bambu Restaurant, Chef Suasa's menu&nbsp;takes you on a&nbsp;whistle-stop tour of South East Asia, with clever presentation and masterful technique. </div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
                <div><strong><em>In March and April,&nbsp;seas restaurant is only available for in-house guests with prior reservations.</em></strong></div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
