                   </div>
                   <div> Only available to in-house guests and High Tea guests, the cliff-front bar, with its jaw-dropping glass floor, is the perfect place to enjoy a&nbsp;tropical cocktail or a selection from the award-winning wine list. Perched on the very&nbsp;edge of the cliff and complete with its own infinity pool, this private haven is perfect&nbsp;for relaxation, a luxury high tea or&nbsp;romantic dinner.&nbsp; </div>
                   <div> &nbsp; </div>
                   <div> Celebrating classics with a twist, the cocktail selection provides the perfect accompaniment to this stunning backdrop. </div>
                   <div> &nbsp; </div>
                   <div> Join us for&nbsp; <strong>Bali's Highest High Tea</strong>&nbsp;at The Cliff Bar.&nbsp; Traditional High Tea served from 11:30 am,&nbsp; <a href="mailto:reservations@theedgebali.com?subject=High%20Tea%20at%20The%20Cliff%20Bar">email us</a>&nbsp;for reservations. </div>
                   <div> &nbsp; </div>
                   <div> |&nbsp; <a href="https://webbox-assets.siteminder.com/assets/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/fd939de9-271c-4ad3-bf78-f6c6e6e3e891.jpeg">Traditional High Tea Menu</a></div>
                </div>
             </div>
          </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container custom-image-left-text-right">
          <div class="row">
             <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6"><img src="//webbox.imgix.net/images/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/7d6bb2ae-fcd8-4bba-bbdf-826bd06c257d.jpg?auto=format,compress&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=entropy" alt="Oneeighty at The edge Luxury Villa Resort, Uluwatu Bali"></div>
             <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <h3><a href="https://www.oneeightybali.com"><strong>ONEEIGHTY°</strong></a></h3>
                <p>International beach-inspired cuisine &amp; drinks&nbsp;| 11:00-21:00 pm</p>
                <p>11:00-17:00 <strong><a href="https://webbox-assets.siteminder.com/assets/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/cc8d5dad-0a1b-4c55-b519-52dedab07643.pdf">Full Menu</a></strong>|&nbsp;17:00-21:00&nbsp; <a href="https://webbox-assets.siteminder.com/assets/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/f81ecad9-cf83-40bc-bca9-054c1025f159.pdf">After Five Menu</a></p>
                <div> oneeighty° is a celebration of sophisticated beach culture set 500ft above the&nbsp;Indian Ocean, with a jaw-dropping glass-bottom sky pool which extends 6.5 metres&nbsp;over the edge of the Uluwatu cliff. Guests of oneeighty° can relax on the cliff-side&nbsp;VIP deck, recline on a sunbed in the sand lounge or take a table at the enclosed bar,&nbsp;all overlooking the most breathtaking 180° panorama. </div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
                <div> By day, the menu reads like a playful ode to classic beachside food, and after 5 pm,&nbsp;the mood changes as oneeighty° transforms into a tranquil oasis with a chilled&nbsp;soundtrack and uplit coconut palms. At the bar, a tempting array of stellar cocktails&nbsp;from the&nbsp;mixologist team back up a Wine Spectator Award-winning wine list. </div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
                <div> Resort guests have private access 08:00 - 11:00 am + exclusive access to the poolside deck&nbsp; </div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
                <p>Take a closer look on&nbsp;<strong><a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/oneeightybali">Instagram</a>&nbsp; or <a href="//www.oneeightybali.com">Book Now</a></strong></p>
             </div>
          </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container custom-image-left-text-right">
          <div class="row">
             <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6"><img src="//webbox.imgix.net/images/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/93e95263-676e-4262-8da6-048e0b045de0.jpg?auto=format,compress&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=entropy" alt="The Club Private Bar at The edge"></div>
             <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <h3><strong>THE CLUB BAR&nbsp;</strong></h3>
                <p>Bar | 12:00 pm - 7:00 pm&nbsp;|&nbsp;</p>
                <div> Relax with a classic cocktail at the bar or enjoy a bottle from our award-winning cellar, surrounded by Bali's best private entertainment complex.&nbsp; </div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
                <div> &nbsp; </div>
             </div>
          </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container custom-image-left-text-right">
          <div class="row">
             <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6"><img src="//webbox.imgix.net/images/kifsqlsyyrpwrthq/c193879d-0add-4dd9-b9a7-1f3610484be4.jpg?auto=format,compress&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=entropy" alt="The Cave"></div>
             <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <h3><strong>THE CAVE&nbsp;- COMING SOON</strong></h3>
                <p>In the midst of the resort is a secret cave revealed only by chance. A stunning subterranean chamber four million years in the making, The&nbsp;Cave&nbsp;will soon be the setting&nbsp;for one of the world’s most unique and breathtaking cocktail &amp; dining experiences.</p>
                <div> Take a closer look on&nbsp; <strong><a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/thecavebali">Instagram</a></strong></div>
             </div>
          </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container custom-text">
          <div class="row">
             <div class="col-xs-12">
                <h1>IN-VILLA DINING</h1>
             </div>
          </div>
       </div>
